Description:
I present you this Art Deco mask, miniature mask brooch, costume jewelry ceramic art, tie tack ready to ship.

For creating this interesting tie tack, brooch pin, I used a miniature ceramic mask handcrafted in my personal studio,  by applying special techniques of pottery  for my miniature figures molds.
The miniature costume jewelry miniature masquerade mask was decorated with a layer of  "antique" patina by using special golden and bronze shades of wax and embellished with 3D swirls made with special metallic colors,  iridiscent colors and high quality Czech glass crystals.
The back of the mask si also decorated with a lot of attention for details by using a delicate embroidery and decorative 3D swirls.

Inside the shipping box, you'll find this fabulous miniature carnival mask gift packed in a delicate organza bag with satin ribbon.
